Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,BARAN'S LAST WILL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You scared us\Nwhen you became unresponsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If this weirdo hadn't come,\Nyou might have never woken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Beast kept casting\NHoimi-type spells on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So I managed to survive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy helped me out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt weird to have my body\Nget fixed by a Heal-type spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm back in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You now have the body\Nof a living organism.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, similar to a Metal Slime\Nor a Metal King Slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why a Hoimi spell works.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm like those creatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You, however, will never fully recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the heavy damage\Nfrom repeated battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,your bones have suffered\Nirreparable damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can probably walk upright,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'll never fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dressed funny,\Nbut you're no ordinary stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. I'm just a member\Nof the Beast King Commandos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gained something wonderful in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. His wounds\Nwere all because of me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'll just be a burden...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but could you take me inside that castle\Nwhere Dai and the others are fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You should return to Queen Flora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave everything for this battle.\NI have to see it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Dai's blade strikes down Ban...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then. I'll lend you my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I refuse,\Nyou'll crawl there yourself, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If need be, I'll be a shield\Nto protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the day you're fully healed\Nand we can settle things again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have you going and dying on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I'll take care of\Nall the enemies you were supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. So Hym is his new friend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You were an enemy once,\Nbut you're a monster with noble spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can join my Beast King Commandos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What is this shrimp babbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a shrimp! Call me "Captain!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You better listen to what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's someone we've all learned to respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... I don't have a badge, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,this will have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?! It won't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. It's a Magic Brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not "you bastard!" Say "Captain!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I never became\Nyour follower, you bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not "you bastard"! Say "Captain"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Has he reached the others yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He should be the greatest help\Nthat they could hope for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Land Rider Larhart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is... Larhart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You bear a resemblance to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you come back from the dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, why are you wearing\Nthe Dark Armour Spear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This was originally mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should it matter if I use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant! Hyunckel...!\NI'm asking what happened to him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He carried out his duty and used\Nall of his strength before falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. That man is immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on! You scared us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So you took on that armour\Nto fight in Hyunckel's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why are you fighting for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Not for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Larhart, fight for only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To pledge my undying allegiance to you,\Nthe successor of the Dragon Knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come before you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! To me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want to be our ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not your ally. Your follower.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Follower?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me to die, and I shall do so gladly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me to fight, and I will face\Neven the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You may use me as you see fit\Nto make the world you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? He's my follower.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You survived a hit from my Hakendisutoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad Mystban,\Nthe heavyweight of the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Master Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to give me your first command.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me to defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A disgraced survivor of the Dragon Masters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,would betray us and bare his fangs\Nagainst me? What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tear you to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to be clear, the Dragon Masters\Nwere never part of the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were direct servants\Nof the Dragon Knight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The three Dragon Masters\Nof the land, sea, and sky!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We never once fought for the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We fought for Master Baran\Nand Master Baran alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To say we betrayed you is the true joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Master Dino. Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mystban is powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I should fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Larhart!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! You're unarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This "tear you to shreds" talk,\Nhow do you intend to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why worry about someone who can't be hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,An afterimage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What we saw being pierced
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,was the shadow Larhart left\Nafter moving at high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, an afterimage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, he's still\Nnot even using his full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell did Hyunckel ever beat him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's strong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He could even be\Non the level of Ron Berku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.49,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}HAKENDISUTORU{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.50,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}GIGA STRASH{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mission should be to defeat\NKing Ban for the surface world humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You must head straight\Ntoward that goal without wavering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am willing to give my life for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the wish your father,\NMaster Baran, left in his last will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was resurrected from death\Nby Master Baran's Dragon Blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there was a letter\Nthat had been left inside my coffin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was Master Baran's last will,\Nwhich he left to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've given all of you Dragon Blood,\Nbut I doubt the others will make it."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"The chances are slim,\Nbut if you should somehow be resurrected,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to help Dino\Nas though you were helping me."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"By that time, I believe\Neither the Dark King or Dino himself
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,will have struck me down\Nand I shall be no more."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Baran was already prepared\Nto sacrifice himself for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Larhart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:12:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I raised you from a young age.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that you feel\Nstrong hatred for the humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, knowing that, I still ask you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should Dino say\Nhe wishes to protect the humans,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}would you please accept and obey him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I believe that child has the power\Nto change humanity itself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my final request,\Nbut the decision is yours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To my other son, Larhart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He was... like a father to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Larhart, you loved my father, too. Deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Dino...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then. I'll give you an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Help Popp and Maam and defeat Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, sir!\N-And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another request.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... don't call me Dino anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing that name is painful.\NIt makes me remember Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Master Dai, the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Leona, Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp! Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'm really\Nleaving things to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to defeat Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't mess up again!\NRelax and go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give the orders!\NYou two, don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Not another one\Nof these personalities!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's a promising rescuer!\NThis might just work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may actually\Nhave to consider the possibility...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of fighting at full strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My true enemy lies ahead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And to reach him, everyone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They've all been wounded...\Nputting everything on the line...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that they could leave me with my power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now I'm going to hit\NDark King Ban with it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how powerful an enemy he is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is... the Tower of Supremacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry on up, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just run out of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice! It's Dark King...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't say anything haughty like,\N"Well done coming this far."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your growth and your numerous rescuers...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,all of it surpassed my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Both Mystban and Kilban{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are being held off\Nby your friends at the moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have been left with no one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I welcome you as\Nan unprecedented challenger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Climb the stairs of the Tower\Nof Supremacy and come before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you a fitting welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, Gomechan, be careful from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh? So you're not alone, Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That woman... She's the princess\Nof Papunica Kingdom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, you can come with whoever you want.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it seems that Dragon Knights have\Na habit of bringing misfortune to women.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not that it matters, I suppose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for, Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, take this knife back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This knife you gave me, it's the last one\Nof the Papunica royal family, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you\Nall of a sudden, Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to what Ban says!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just toying with you\Nbefore the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this\Nbecause I'm saying goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The opposite?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, aside from Master's Feathers,\Nyou're basically unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be using my Dragonic Aura at\Nfull strength, so I can't use this knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you carry it,\Nat least you'll have a weapon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying\NI should look after myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ban we're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee I can win alone\Nor even protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to fight with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to face danger,\Ndo it with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sorry. That's asking too much.\N-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is kind of like\Nthe first time we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:19:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I attached the knife to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And wasn't it the three of us\Nback on Dermline Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and you and Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You struggled against one Scorpion,\Nyet now you're fighting the Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart was seriously pounding back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just going to a cave on my island,\Nbut it felt like my chest would explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How about now? Is your heart pounding?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart's pounding...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's different from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart isn't dancing.\NIt's more like it feels tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like it was back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:20:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai isn't just an adventurous\Nyoung boy anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's still tiny, but he's a Hero\Ncarrying the hopes of all humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He must be feeling\Ntremendous pressure on his shoulders.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to help him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. Even if I can't help,\NI have to ease his burden any way I can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that someday Dai can travel the world\Nwith a light heart once again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is an unexpected turn of events.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never expected it to act on its own.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, if they were attacked, then they...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that?! What just grabbed Leona?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was that Ban's doing?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:17.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:28.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:36.02,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:45.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:49.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:55.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:23:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:23:02.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:09.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:14.97,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:20.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:26.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.78,0:23:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and Leona race up the Tower\Nof Supremacy to face Dark King Ban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Leona is suddenly attacked\Nby mysterious tentacles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.12,0:23:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai follows after, only to reach\Nthe heart of Ban Palace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.42,0:23:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There he finds something\Neven Ban wasn't expecting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.63,0:23:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What will happen to Dai and Leona?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.68,0:23:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Rise, Knight of Destiny"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.35,0:24:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:02.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,
